column5: http://www.cbc.ca/testthenation/  This is a TV program that tests your IQ... I will be participating.. anyone else? Should be interesting.. I have had IQ tests before, and always did well... I wonder if I have gotten stupider  Gerritt.
Here is the direct link to the Score Card.....   http://www.cbc.ca/testthenation/takethetes...n_scorecard.pdf  Good luck to those that take part!  Gerritt.
Not me, I already know how smart I'm not...don't need and IQ test to tell me that  Maureen
Geez....not sure that I want to find out either. I just wanna go fishin'
No, my last three tests were exactly the same, spaced out over 30 years. Guess beer doesnt make you dummer.
That scorecard doesn't appear to be useable.
Works here and I printed it off etc... it is a PDF file meaning you need adobe acrobat installed.... go here for acrobat.. www.adobe.com   Gerritt.
Must buy printer.
I'll stick with "Deal, or no Deal".  But thanks for the heads up Gerritt.
I took the test online since it was so much quicker. At least I accurately predicted my I.Q. LOL

Hey I did it on the net, and I guessed I would get 120 and ended up with 117. I'm sure I missed at least 5 questions on time. Some questions I didn't get to read all the answers.  I guess I'm still above average.
Awesome.... I had 1!!!! i guess i am the best in the country right?... Atleast I am with the national average of people though... how does someone get 100%???? lol
Geez, that was tougher/more fun than I expected it to be. Apparently, my language skills aren't so hot, and my memory sucks.
I believe the correct term is "more stupid" so the answer to that question would be yes!  (just kidding.....sorry couldn't resist   )
Well not any smarter, nor any dumber....just slower!!!!!!!!!
Interesting test...I estimated 115 and got 118.  It was tougher than I thought it would be!

Geesh!!! You guys are a bunch of brainiacs!  I kinda feel like Hank on the TV show "Corner Gas."  I had a hard time trying to beat the clock on some of them and failed to answer on time. I faired in the average group of people.
guessed 120 got 115

The wife and I played last night on TV. We actually had a good time playing. Sucked on the memory parts... gettin' old I guess... pulled off a 122... stupid memory questions brought me down... and who knew that baby lavalife needed attention paid to it... oh well fun nonetheless!!!

Well, I was gonna watch the show, but it was on at the same time as The Simpsons and.... well you know! Just took the quiz online, scored 135! Man, I thought I'd maybe break into the 90's but... think I'll ask for a raise!LOL HH

didn't get to do it last night as i was working so i just took it, i said average (100) and scored 132, I"M A GENIUS, if only my high school advisor could see me know,  now if only i used my mind for good instead of evil.....mmmwwaaahahahahahahahah
